### C. DB Schema Summary

| Model | Table | Phase | Key Relations |
|---|---|---|---|
| `User` | `users` | 1 | → UserRole, RefreshToken, AuditLog, StudentProfile, Bed (all others) |
| `Role` | `roles` | 1 | → UserRole, RolePermission |
| `Permission` | `permissions` | 1 | → RolePermission |
| `UserRole` | `user_roles` | 1 | User ↔ Role (with optional hostelId scope) |
| `RolePermission` | `role_permissions` | 1 | Role ↔ Permission M:N |
| `RefreshToken` | `refresh_tokens` | 1 | → User; stores bcrypt hash |
| `AuditLog` | `audit_logs` | 1 | → User (nullable); JSON details |
| `Hostel` | `hostels` | 2 | → Room[], UserRole[], Building? |
| `Room` | `rooms` | 2 | → Hostel, Bed[] |
| `Bed` | `beds` | 2 | → Room, User? (student), BedAssignment[] |
| `Building` | `buildings` | 3 | → Hostel[], BuildingPolicy[], PolicySnapshot[], Notice[] |
| `BuildingPolicy` | `building_policies` | 3 | → Building; versioned, isActive flag |
| `StudentProfile` | `student_profiles` | 3 | 1:1 → User; 45+ fields |
| `GuardianLink` | `guardian_links` | 3 | Student ↔ Guardian (User) M:N |
| `BedAssignment` | `bed_assignments` | 3 | Student → Bed; lifecycle: ACTIVE/VACATED/TRANSFERRED/EXPIRED |
| `LeaveRequest` | `leave_requests` | 4 | → Student, Hostel, Warden, Parent; dual-approval |
| `Complaint` | `complaints` + `complaint_comments` | 4 | → Student, Hostel, AssignedTo |
| `Notice` | `notices` + `notice_recipients` | 4 | Scoped: ALL/BUILDING/HOSTEL |
| `GateEntry` | `gate_entries` | 4 | → Student, LeaveRequest (linked), PolicySnapshot |
| `GatePass` | `gate_passes` | 4 | → Student, ApprovedBy |
| `PolicySnapshot` | `policy_snapshots` | 5 | Immutable copy at gate scan time → GateEntry, Violation |
| `Violation` | `violations` | 5 | → Student, GateEntry, PolicySnapshot; escalation state machine |
| `Notification` | `notifications` | 5 | → User (recipient), Violation?, GateEntry? |
| `HostelRegistration` | `hostel_registrations` | 6 | → Student, Hostel, Reviewer; 5 declaration flags |
| `RegistrationFee` | `registration_fees` | 6 | → HostelRegistration, RecordedBy |

**Enums (20+):** `UserStatus`, `HostelType`, `HostelStatus`, `RoomType`, `RoomStatus`, `BedStatus`, `BuildingStatus`, `AssignmentStatus`, `LeaveType`, `LeaveStatus`, `ComplaintCategory`, `ComplaintPriority`, `ComplaintStatus`, `NoticePriority`, `NoticeScope`, `GateEntryType`, `GatePassStatus`, `ViolationType`, `EscalationState`, `NotificationState`, `NotificationChannel`, `AdmissionMode`, `RegistrationStatus`, `FeeType`

