### D. Config & Environment Variables

| Variable | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `NODE_ENV` | Environment: development/production |
| `APP_PORT` | API port (default 3001) |
| `APP_URL` | Self-referential URL |
| `FRONTEND_URL` | Allowed CORS origin |
| `DB_HOST`, `DB_PORT`, `DB_USER`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `DB_NAME` | Database connection parts |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Prisma connection string (composed from above) |
| `REDIS_HOST`, `REDIS_PORT`, `REDIS_PASSWORD` | Redis connection |
| `JWT_SECRET` | HS256 signing secret (min 32 chars) |
| `JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRY` | Access token expiry (default `15m`) |
| `JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRY` | Refresh token expiry (default `7d`) |
| `THROTTLE_TTL`, `THROTTLE_LIMIT` | Global rate limiter config |
| `SEED_ADMIN_EMAIL` | Seeded super admin email |
| `SEED_ADMIN_PASSWORD` | Seeded super admin password |
| *(commented)* `STORAGE_ENDPOINT`, `STORAGE_BUCKET`, etc. | S3 storage (not yet used) |
| *(commented)* `RAZORPAY_KEY_ID`, `RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET`, etc. | Payment gateway (not yet used) |
| *(commented)* `SMTP_HOST`, `SMTP_PORT`, `SMTP_USER`, `SMS_PROVIDER_API_KEY` | Email/SMS (not yet used) |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Never print or log `JWT_SECRET`, `DB_PASSWORD`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET`, or `SMTP_PASSWORD`. The `AuditService` already redacts `password` and `token` fields from audit log details.
